script.name: plugin.stationmgr.move
script.sourceplaintext:
* ======================================== * Station Manager Move Script * ======================================== * Controls the movement of ships when being managed * ======================================== * Author: Cycrow * Date: 2018/05/25 * ========================================
do if [DOCKEDAT] == $destination return null skip if [HOMEBASE] -> exists return null skip if $destination -> exists return null skip if [HOMEBASE] -> is of class Station return null
$DEBUG = [HOMEBASE] -> get local variable: name='DEBUG.stationmgr' do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Moving ship: %s, destination=%s', [HOMEBASE], [THIS], $destination, null, null
[THIS] ->add secondary signal: signal=SIGNAL_KILLED, script=plugin.stationmgr.ship.signal, prio=100, name='station.manager' [THIS] ->add secondary signal: signal=SIGNAL_ATTACKED, script=plugin.stationmgr.ship.attacked, prio=100, name='station.manager' [THIS] ->set trade report use homebase enabled [TRUE]
[THIS] ->set is being managed: on=[TRUE] [THIS] ->set managed by homebase: [TRUE] [THIS] ->set destination to $destination [THIS] ->set attacked response type (Player Only): [Attacked.Flee] if not [THIS] -> is emergency jump activated [THIS] ->set emergency jump active: [TRUE] [THIS] ->autojump emergency jump shield threshold= 80% end
$blacklst = [HOMEBASE] -> get local variable: name='egosoft.stationmgr.blacklist' gosub sub.SetCommand
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Moving ship, blacklist=%s', [HOMEBASE], $blacklst, $ret, null, null
$home.energy = [HOMEBASE] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $home.sector = [HOMEBASE] -> get sector $home.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $home.sector $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector
$exclude = table alloc $table.allow = table alloc $table.allow[$home.sector] = [TRUE]
if $dest.sector != [SECTOR] do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Moving ship: %s, current sector=%s, dest=%s', [HOMEBASE], [THIS], [SECTOR], $dest.sector, null
if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Navigation Command Software MK1 in cargo bay @ $plotted.route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] Allow Table=$table.allow
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Plotted route: %s', [HOMEBASE], $plotted.route, [SECTOR], $dest.sector, null
if $plotted.route == [TRUE] return FLRET_OK else if $plotted.route @ = wait 100 ms
$jump.target = $plotted.route[0] $jump.sector = $jump.target -> get sector
$sub.Sector = $jump.sector gosub sub.GetNeededEnergy
do if [DOCKEDAT] -> exists gosub sub.ResupplyAtDocked
$no.try = 0 while [TRUE] inc $no.try = @ = wait 1000 ms
if $no.try > 100 return FLRET_NOPATH end
$extra.wait = ( $no.try / 5 ) * 500 do if $extra.wait @ = wait $extra.wait ms
* check if we have enoguh energy $dest.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $jump.sector $energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $jump.sector $got.energy = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $got.energy >= $energy break end
$need.energy = $energy - $got.energy
* need to find some * if we can fly to the destination, then just pick the if closer @ = wait 100 ms @ if [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$table.allow do if $dest.jumps <= 1 break $max.jumps = $dest.jumps - 1 else $max.jumps = [HOMEBASE] ->get max buy jumps end
$home.energy = [HOMEBASE] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $home.route = null if $home.energy >= $need.energy @ $home.route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=[HOMEBASE] Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$table.allow if $home.route == [TRUE] $spp = [HOMEBASE] gosub sub.Resupply do if $bought > 0 continue else if $home.route $home.target = $home.route[0] $home.route.sector = $home.target -> get sector $home.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $home.route.sector if $home.jumps <= 1 $spp = [HOMEBASE] gosub sub.Resupply do if $bought > 0 continue end if $max.jumps > $home.jumps $max.jumps = $home.jumps - 1 end end end
if [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay gosub sub.FindSPP if $spp -> exists gosub sub.Resupply do if $bought > 0 continue else if $home.route $spp = [HOMEBASE] gosub sub.Resupply do if $bought > 0 continue end end
@ = wait 100 ms @ if [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$table.allow break end
* consider removing wares to make room gosub sub.DumpWares
@ = wait 500 ms end
@ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$table.allow @ = wait 200 ms return FLRET_NOPATH end [THIS] ->set destination to $destination $got.energy = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $jump.sector if $got.energy >= $energy $pos = $destination -> get position as array append $dest.sector to array $pos gosub sub.SetCommand @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.jumptogate.nearest : targetpos=$pos should followers jump too=[TRUE] else $sub.Jump = $destination gosub sub.JumpToSector end end end end end
do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Attempting to just fly', [HOMEBASE], $plotted.route, [SECTOR], $dest.sector, null
@ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$destination Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[FALSE] Additional Blacklist=$blacklst Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$table.allow @ = wait 200 ms return FLRET_NOPATH end
gosub sub.SetCommand if $destination -> is of class Debris $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$dest.sector else if $destination -> is of class Asteroid $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$dest.sector else if $destination -> is of class Sector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$destination else if $destination -> is of class Station @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$destination else $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$dest.sector $best.price = null end do if $DEBUG write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Finishing moving ship: %s, ret=%s', [HOMEBASE], [THIS], $ret, null, null return $ret
sub.CheckInterupt: endsub
sub.DumpWares: $max.jumps = [HOMEBASE] ->get max buy jumps $max.needed = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=$max.jumps $got.energy = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $max.needed = $max.needed - $got.energy if $max.needed > 0 $energy.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $max.needed > $energy.free $ware.vol = get volume of ware Energy Cells $space.needed = ( $max.needed - $energy.free ) * $ware.vol $aTradeable = [THIS] -> get tradeable ware array from ship $best.ware = null $best.price = null $i = size of array $aTradeable while $i dec $i = $ship.ware = $aTradeable[$i] $ware.vol = get volume of ware $ship.ware if $ship.ware != Energy Cells AND $ware.vol > 0 $ware.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ship.ware in cargo bay if $ware.amt > 0 $ware.price = get average price of ware $ship.ware if ! $best.ware OR ! $best.price OR $best.price > $ware.price $best.ware = $ship.ware $best.price = $ware.price end end end end if $best.ware $ware.vol = get volume of ware $best.ware $remove = - ( ( $space.needed / $ware.vol ) + 1 ) = [THIS] -> add $remove units of $best.ware end end end endsub
sub.SetCommand: if $a.type == 'home' [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_RETURN_HOME target=null target2=null par1=null par2=null else if $a.type == 'mine' $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_MINE_HOMEBASE $read.text = read text: page=2010 id=100031 [THIS] ->set command display override: text=$read.text $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2154, $dest.sector, $ware, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text else if $a.type == 'salvage' $dest.sector = $destination -> get sector $ware = $destination -> get ware type code of object [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_COLLECT_WARE $read.text = read text: page=2010 id=100031 [THIS] ->set command display override: text=$read.text $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2156, $ware, $dest.sector, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text else [THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_DOCKAT $read.text = read text: page=2010 id=100031 [THIS] ->set command display override: text=$read.text if $destination == [HOMEBASE] $read.text = read text: page=2010 id=1 else if $a.type == 'buy' $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2082, $ware, $ware.amt, null, null, null else if $a.type == 'sell' $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2083, $ware, $ware.amt, null, null, null else if $a.type == 'repair' $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2084, $destination, null, null, null, null else if $a.type == 'upgrade' $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2085, $ware, $destination, null, null, null end [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text end endsub
sub.ResupplyAtDocked: if [DOCKEDAT] $dock.owner = [DOCKEDAT] -> get owner race $sub.Sector = $jump.sector gosub sub.GetNeededEnergy $got.energy = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $needed = $ret.Energy - $got.energy if $needed > 0 if [OWNER] == $dock.owner $bought = [THIS] ->load $needed units of Energy Cells, ignore minimum=[TRUE] else $bought = [THIS] -> buy $needed units of Energy Cells end @ = wait 1000 ms end end endsub
sub.Resupply: [THIS] ->set destination to $spp $sub.Jump = $spp gosub sub.JumpToSector gosub sub.SetCommand $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2091, $spp, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text while [DOCKEDAT] != $spp @ = wait 100 ms @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$spp do if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH endsub end gosub sub.ResupplyAtDocked endsub
sub.FindSPP: $spp = null
* calculate how many jumps max we can buy $energy.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy.got = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $max.energy = $energy.got + $energy.free $per.sector = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy per sector $energy.jumps = ( $max.energy / $per.sector ) - 1 do if $max.jumps > $energy.jumps $max.jumps = $energy.jumps
if $max.jumps > 1 $price = get max price of ware Energy Cells while [TRUE] @ = wait 500 ms $spp = find station: product Energy Cells with min. jumps: max.price=$price, amount=$need.energy, max.jumps=$max.jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$exclude skip if $spp -> exists break
$spp.sector = $spp -> get sector $dest.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $spp.sector if $spp.sector ->is sector in blocked blacklist $exclude[$spp.sector] = [TRUE] else if $dest.jumps >= $jumps $exclude[$spp.sector] = [TRUE] else if $dest.jumps >= $home.jumps $exclude[$spp.sector] = [TRUE] @ else if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$spp Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$blacklst $exclude[$spp.sector] = [TRUE] else break end end end
if $spp -> exists $spp.price = $spp -> get price of ware Energy Cells $spp.sector = $spp -> get sector $spp.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $spp.sector
while [TRUE] @ = wait 100 ms $better.spp = find station: product Energy Cells with best price: max.price=$spp.price, amount=$need.energy, max.jumps=$spp.jumps, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=[THIS], exclude array=$exclude skip if $better.spp -> exists break $bspp.sector = $better.spp -> get sector $dest.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $bspp.sector if $bspp.sector ->is sector in blocked blacklist $exclude[$bspp.sector] = [TRUE] else if $dest.jumps >= $jumps $exclude[$bspp.sector] = [TRUE] else if $dest.jumps >= $home.jumps $exclude[$bspp.sector] = [TRUE] @ else if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$better.spp Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=$blacklst $exclude[$bspp.sector] = [TRUE] else break end end
do if $better.spp -> exists $spp = $better.spp end
endsub
sub.GetNeededEnergy: if $destination == [HOMEBASE] $ret.Energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $sub.Sector else $ret.Energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $sub.Sector $ret.Energy = $ret.Energy * 2 $resupply = [THIS] -> get jumpdrive fuel resupply if $resupply $per.sector = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy per sector $min.energy = $resupply * $per.sector else $min.energy = 400 end $ret.Energy = get maximum, $ret.Energy, $min.energy, null, null, null end endsub
sub.JumpToSector: $sub.Sector = $sub.Jump -> get sector @ $jumpable.sector = [THIS] -> call script !lib.ship.getclosestjump : Desintation=$sub.Jump Exclude Trans-Orbital=[TRUE]
gosub sub.SetCommand if $jumpable.sector == $sub.Sector $pos = $sub.Jump -> get position as array append $sub.Sector to array $pos @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.jumptogate.nearest : targetpos=$pos should followers jump too=[TRUE]
else if $jumpable.sector $gate = get next gate on route from $jumpable.sector to $sub.Sector if $gate -> exists @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.jump : gate or sector=$gate followers should jump too=[TRUE] else @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.jump : gate or sector=$jumpable.sector followers should jump too=[TRUE] end end endsub return null
